data.description: This beautifully maintained 3 bed 2 bath single family home is a must see! It's located in the highly sought-after Hawksmoor community which is nestled within Winter Garden's popular Horizon West area. As you enter the home, you're greeted with an open concept layout, high ceilings, split bedroom floor plan, and lots of natural light! The kitchen boasts of dark 42" cabinets, Stainless steel appliances, beautiful Quartz countertops and ample storage space. The extra large kitchen island will surely make entertaining friends and family a breeze! The Primary bedroom is tucked away in the rear of the home featuring 10 ft. coffered ceilings, large walk-in closet, an en suite bathroom with dual sinks, quartz countertops, and a spacious shower with a full tile wall. The two secondary bedrooms and full bathroom are located towards the front of the home away from the main living area providing privacy and easy access for guests. The home also includes Solar Panels, a full-home water filtration/water softening system, and Smart Thermostat. The community is zoned for top-notch schools and offers amenities the whole family can enjoy such as a Fitness Center, Walking trails, a fabulous Clubhouse, a Resort-style pool and a splash pad. Easy access to FL-429 and the Turnpike means you're minutes away from Disney's Magic Kingdom, world-class dining, shopping, and all other major attractions. Come and enjoy all the beauty that Central Florida has to offer!
